ale literacy is 56%. In Ramdass, 14% of the population is under 6 years of age. Ramdass city belongs to the [[Jat]] [[Sikh]] Bal clan. \n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Amritsar district}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Amritsar district]]\n\n{{PunjabIN-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "119.160.119.66", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "(\u2192\u200eDemographics)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramdass"}
